X3DLoader binaries VC9.0
========================

Installation
============

	Requirements:
	The X3DLoader library 32-bit binaries for x86 architecture 	require the 
	'Visual C++ 2008 Redistributable Package (x86)' installed on the target 
	machine. 
  
	The X3DLoader library 64-bit binaries for x86_64 architecture require the 
	'Visual C++ 2008 Redistributable Package (x64)' installed on the target 
	machine. 

Package directory layout
========================
   /doc
     /html              :  API HTML documentation.
   /bin		            :  X3DLoader binary DLLs with dependend libs and 
                           example applications
   /lib                 :  Archive libraries for linkage
   /data                :  Example X3D files
   /include             :  Header files

   
Usage
=====
	Please refer to doc/html/index.html for information on how to use the 
	X3DLoader library.


